OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,FThe US and Iran have "agreed upon the
OL,7,Ftext" of a deal and peace has "never
OL,8,Fbeen this close as it is now",
OL,9,FPakistan's prime minister has said.
OL,11,FPakistan has been leading efforts to
OL,12,Fmediate a deal between the two
OL,13,Fcountries since late March, weeks
OL,14,Fafter the conflict began on February
OL,15,F28.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
