CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,F"Amid ongoing intense mediation
OL,7,Fefforts by Pakistan, we are fully
OL,8,Faware of incessant misinformation
OL,9,Fcampaign being waged by those who want
OL,10,Fto sabotage the peace deal," Shehbaz
OL,11,FSharif posted on X on Friday.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,F"Setting aside the noise, we can
OL,7,Fconfirm that a final, agreed upon text
OL,8,Fof the peace deal has been reached and
OL,9,FPakistan is now working closely with
OL,10,Fboth sides to finalize the next steps.
OL,12,F"Peace has never been this close as it
OL,13,Fis now."
OL,15,FAlthough neither Iran nor the US have
OL,16,Fcommented on Sharif's claims, Iranian
OL,17,FForeign Minister Abbas Araghchi posted
OL,18,Fearlier on Friday that an agreement
OL,19,F"has never been closer".
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,FOn his post on X, Aragchi added: "all
OL,7,Fdetails will be shared with the public
OL,8,Fin due course."
OL,10,FUS President Donald Trump shared
OL,11,FAraghchi's post on his own social
OL,12,Fmedia page, Truth Social.
OL,14,FThe apparent breakthrough in
OL,15,Fnegotiations comes after Iran
OL,16,Fexchanged fire with the US and Israel
OL,17,Fover three days this week, threatening
OL,18,Fto return the region to full-scale war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,FTrump has said multiple times in
OL,7,Frecent weeks that the countries were
OL,8,Fon the cusp of a deal, despite the
OL,9,Fattacks, which happened even though a
OL,10,Fceasefire has been in place since
OL,11,FApril 7.
OL,13,FRegional officials in Pakistan said
OL,14,Fthe emerging deal is expected to pave
OL,15,Fthe way for reopening the Strait of
OL,16,FHormuz, the phased lifting of
OL,17,Fsanctions on Iran, and the release of
OL,18,Ffrozen Iranian assets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,FThese officials spoke on condition of
OL,7,Fanonymity because of the sensitivity
OL,8,Fof the negotiations.
OL,10,FA senior US official said key terms in
OL,11,Fthe emerging agreement include the
OL,12,Fremoval and destruction of Iran's
OL,13,Fnuclear material and the dismantling
OL,14,Fof Tehran's nuclear program, as well
OL,15,Fas Iran agreeing not to fund terrorist
OL,16,Fgroups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
