PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,FUnderscoring the fragility of the
OL,7,Ftalks, Trump on Friday lashed out at
OL,8,FIranian officials on social media,
OL,9,Fclaiming that terms shared with the
OL,10,Fcountry's media were fake.
OL,12,F"What they said, including their weak
OL,13,Fand pathetic statement on having a
OL,14,Fdeal, bears no relation to the truth.
OL,15,FVery dishonourable people to deal
OL,16,Fwith," Trump wrote on Truth Social.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
