FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,F"With them, there is no such thing as
OL,7,Fdealing in good faith. AMAZING! Also,
OL,8,Ftheir totally rebuffed Drone attack
OL,9,Flast night against Indian Ships
OL,10,Fleaving the Hormuz Strait is TOTALLY
OL,11,FUNACCEPTABLE.
OL,13,F"They better get their act together,
OL,14,Fand FAST!"
OL,16,FUS Vice President JD Vance also posted
OL,17,Fabout the deal on Friday, claiming
OL,18,Fthat it "has the potential to remake
OL,19,Fthe region and lead to lasting peace".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
