PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Israeli Prime Minister
OL,7,FBenjamin Netanyahu has declared that
OL,8,FIsrael is not party to the deal being
OL,9,Fnegotiated, but said he and Trump were
OL,10,Fin "full agreement" that Iran must not
OL,11,Fhave nuclear weapons.
OL,13,FIran has insisted that any deal to end
OL,14,Fthe war must also end fighting in
OL,15,FLebanon between its ally militia
OL,16,FHezbollah and Israel.
OL,26,@rD@DOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
