CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1781381159
OL,3,CUS and Iran 'agree on text of peace
OL,4,Cdeal' says Pakistan's prime minister
OL,6,FNetanyahu has appeared to be intent on
OL,7,Fpursuing his goal of destroying the
OL,8,Fmilitant group, which has so-far
OL,9,Fcomplicated the negotiations between
OL,10,FIran and the US.
OL,12,FThe deal was largely being brokered by
OL,13,FPakistan, led by its army chief Field
OL,14,FMarshal Asim Munir, the regional
OL,15,Fofficials said, with backing from
OL,16,FSaudi Arabia, Turkey, Egypt, and Qatar.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
